  <Title>Itemshop Release</Title>
  <Type>1</Type>
  <Content>&lt;b&gt;Itemshop will be released on Monday October 6th&lt;/b&gt;

New Items will be located in Costume, Hats, Weapon, Hairstyle &amp; Events.

&lt;b&gt;Weapon Skins&lt;/b&gt;
This item will allow you to change the look of your one-handed weapon; the name along with all stats/attributes will remain the same. Once the weapon is changed it is no longer bankable. Equip the weapon you want to change, then use this item. Can only be used on one weapon at a time.

&lt;b&gt;Random Mech Box&lt;/b&gt;
Will receive 1 of 6 Mechs. When equipped, players will be transformed into a Mech! Random Mech Box is NOT droppable, the items inside are droppable.

